{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/Front-end/css_/css_4/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<blockquote>\n<p>understanding CSS</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://internetingishard.com/\">reference</a></li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<h3>Practice making a Menu</h3>\n<h4>Navigation Menu</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>should almost always be <strong>marked up as a &#x3C; ul> list</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>these semantics make the site's navigation much <em>more accessible to search engine</em></p>\n<pre class=\"andromeda vscode-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><code class=\"vscode-highlight-code\"><span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk8\">ul</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">class</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk12\">&#39;menu&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk8\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk8\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">href</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk12\">&#39;#&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;Blog&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk8\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk8\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk8\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk8\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">href</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk12\">&#39;#&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;About&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk8\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk8\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk8\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk8\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">href</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk12\">&#39;#&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;Subscribe&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk8\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk8\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk8\">ul</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>set the <strong>&#x3C; li> items as inline boxes</strong>: <code>display: inline</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>use child selectors <code>></code> to only select the direct &#x3C; li> items under the menu</p>\n<pre class=\"andromeda vscode-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"vscode-highlight-code\"><span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk7\">.menu</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    display: </span><span class=\"mtk5\">inline</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    margin-right: </span><span class=\"mtk6\">0</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk7\">.menu</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk8\">li</span><span class=\"mtk7\">:last-of-type</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    margin-right: </span><span class=\"mtk6\">0</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><s