 class=\"mtk1\">            &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk8\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk8\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">href</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk12\">&#39;#&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;Travel&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk8\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk8\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">            &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk8\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk8\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">href</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk12\">&#39;#&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;Lifestyle&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk8\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk8\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">            &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk8\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk8\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">href</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk12\">&#39;#&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;Quotes&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk8\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk8\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        &lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk8\">ul</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    &lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk8\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk4\">&lt;!-- where other menu items are (part of navigation menu)--&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"vscode-highlight-line\"><span class=\"mtk1\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk8\">ul</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></